(1, 1, '2014-12-09 20:10:51', '2014-12-09 20:10:51', '<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://law.localhost/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/lawoffice.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-11 size-full" src="http://law.localhost/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/lawoffice.jpg" alt="lawoffice" width="800" height="550" /></a></p>\r\nThe Romaker Law Firm exists with one mission in mind: the exclusive, skilled, and zealous representation of individuals – not corporations or insurance companies – in all matters of workers’ compensation and personal injury. There are no conflicts or compromises here. We are also proud to say that our attorneys dedicate themselves fully to the practice of representing plaintiffs and petitioners. We competently take cases from intake to judgment, all the while advocating for our clients’ rights. As a result, The Romaker Law Firm is respected by clients and opponents alike.\r\n\r\nWe also have a successful track record. Indeed, over the last 20 years, our attorneys have recovered millions of dollars for thousands of clients. Winning money for our clients, however, is not the only way we measure success. Our firm’s attorneys have also had success reinstating employees and securing payment of expensive medical treatment, including rehabilitation and necessary surgery. In other words, whether we seek monetary relief for our clients or any other remedy, our attorneys fight vigorously, through mediation, arbitration, and litigation, to achieve the best results.\r\n\r\nRead on to learn more about The Romaker Law Firm and how we can help you. For more information, you can fill out and submit the form to the right, or contact us at 312-377-7000. Either way, we welcome the opportunity to hear from you about your situation and any questions you may have.', 'Romaker Law Firm', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world', '', '', '2014-12-11 11:57:29', '2014-12-11 11:57:29', '', 0, 'http://law.localhost/wordpress/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
